                {
                    "Content": "<h2>Easy to Use with Reliability You Can Count On</h2>\r\n<p>MatterControl T10 has all the same great features as MatterControl Touch with even more capabilities. A high definition 10.6\" touchscreen allows controlling your printer to be seamless and rendering designs sharp. A powerful 2Ghz Octa-Core processor enables faster on board slicing and quick access to design files stored on MatterControl Cloud Sync. The software development team at MatterHackers has optimized the device performance to ensure stability, even for long prints.</p>", 
                    "ElementCode": "PEFFJP", 
                    "Images": [], 
                    "Type": "text"
                }, 
                {
                    "Content": "<p style='text-align:center;'><img title='MatterControl Touch T10 - 10.6\" Standalone 3D Printer Controller' src='https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/MaGzJictCAE-bJEcXwrd2WXAmM8E81U8EhXp7P1Z_ExD4oRFnDt7QJO72NHIWyfc_w5uxrosob3p7odAHnC0sNz3QQ'></p>", 
                    "ElementCode": "RCHYCU", 
                    "Images": [
                        {
                            "ImageFile": "/mh-product-images/prod/legacy_MaGzJictCAE-bJEcXwrd2WXAmM8E81U8EhXp7P1Z_ExD4oRFnDt7QJO72NHIWyfc_w5uxrosob3p7odAHnC0sNz3QQ", 
                            "ImageUrl": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/RVstvi8Ope3EIZoeCsUnLMyL93EEmZ4re60NGAwy-wWHoEj20Yl4MTDD2mHznaKEjhYwBURmuYOkd-hkO2_T-j7R", 
                            "IsFeatured": false
                        }
                    ], 
                    "Type": "text"
                }, 
                {
                    "Content": "<h2>Give Your 3D Printer a Brain with MatterControl Touch</h2>\r\n<p>MatterControl T10 gives your 3D printer a life of its own. With it you can reclaim your laptop and eliminate the &lsquo;SD card shuffle&rsquo; between your computer and printer. You get the full-featured experience of printing with MatterControl without relying on a desktop computer. Curious how your print is going? You can check the progress wherever you are via the web with the free MatterControl Cloud Sync. MatterControl T10 can even text or email you a picture of your completed print the moment it&rsquo;s finished. MatterControl supports over 40 models of 3D printers, and that list is always growing.</p>", 
                    "ElementCode": "LTECKK", 
                    "Images": [], 
                    "Type": "text"
                }, 
                {
                    "Content": "<h2>How It Works</h2>\r\n<p>Plug in your MatterControl Touch, connect via USB to any compatible 3D printer and then follow the simple setup wizard. Congratulations! You now have a standalone 3D printer capable of handling your 3D printing workflow from start to finish. Sign-in to send and receive print jobs, or download models directly from the web.</p>", 
                    "ElementCode": "W9YJHQ", 
                    "Images": [], 
                    "Type": "text"
                }, 
                {
                    "Content": "<h2>Getting Started With MatterControl Touch</h2>", 
                    "ElementCode": "1QV21N", 
                    "Images": [], 
                    "Type": "text"
                }, 
                {
                    "Content": "<div class=\"video-container\">\n<div class=\"embed-youtube\" data-embed=\"nposQEgTc_s\" data-size=\"lg\">\n</div>\n</div>", 
                    "ElementCode": "3VFX7U", 
                    "Images": [], 
                    "Type": "html"
                }, 
                {
                    "Content": "<h2>MatterControl T10 Features</h2>\r\n<p>MatterControl T10 integrates every component that you love about MatterControl and includes some exciting new features.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Simple Setup</strong> - Preloaded configurations make setting up your 3D printer a snap - plug it in and start printing in minutes.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Integrated Slicing</strong> - Give your printer the ability to directly generate print files from 3D models using MatterSlice.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Remote Print Monitoring</strong> - Keep an eye on your 3D prints from afar using your phone or any web-enabled device using MatterControl Cloud Sync.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Automatic Print Leveling</strong> - Use software-based leveling to achieve that perfect first layer.</p>\r\n<p><strong>SMS / Email Notifications</strong> - Have your printer send a text message or email alert with a photo of your finished part.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Onboard Camera</strong> - Take a picture of your finished print or check on the status while printing with the onboard 5.0 megapixel camera.</p>", 
                    "ElementCode": "3GJPA8", 
                    "Images": [], 
                    "Type": "text"
                }, 
                {
                    "Content": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img title=\"\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/WbbGR9XxfVOd8GZbNTR_EBQXxp2thlVEYWjEQMaSjSAui_HtvvSTsAuIBTmeYP1qDOD8PH4YHuozyOxc5zpr7VIuZg\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Text message notifications alert you when your print is complete.&nbsp;</em></p>", 
                    "ElementCode": "XGOAWF", 
                    "Images": [
                        {
                            "ImageFile": "/mh-product-images/prod/legacy_WbbGR9XxfVOd8GZbNTR_EBQXxp2thlVEYWjEQMaSjSAui_HtvvSTsAuIBTmeYP1qDOD8PH4YHuozyOxc5zpr7VIuZg", 
                            "ImageUrl": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/2NE4ZJsmH2CuQQqOqsPlnJewjIz5Yygk97H5qth9g5mWFjQA6u03CHAV6zOviTtl6gwtYe5tOQvV9ADeJjoiOBDm", 
                            "IsFeatured": false
                        }
                    ], 
                    "Type": "text"
                }, 
                {
                    "Content": "<p><strong><strong>Free Updates</strong>&nbsp;-&nbsp;</strong>MatterControl is a continuously improving platform and staying up to date with the latest developments is just a simple click away.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Open Source Software</strong>&nbsp;- MatterControl T10 is powered by open source software and libraries, including MatterControl, MatterSlice, the&nbsp;agg-sharp graphics engine, and the Android operating system.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Wifi Enabled, Not Required</strong>&nbsp;- Enjoy a fully standalone experience or connect your printer to the web to take advantage of <a title=\"MatterControl Sync\" href=\"http://sync.mattercontrol.com/\" target=\"_blank\">MatterControl Cloud Sync</a> features.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Send Files over the Web</strong>&nbsp;- Send designs to your printer from anywhere, or transfer models between printers using&nbsp;MatterControl Cloud Library. SD Cards not required.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Model Editing Tools</strong>&nbsp;- Make changes to your 3D model quickly and easily prior to printing. Rotate, scale,&nbsp;mirror&nbsp;and position your models for the perfect print.</p>\r\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-de3e4705-136a-3d4d-4e64-b1a58c286096\"><strong>Full Preview</strong>&nbsp;- Preview and interact with 3D models prior to printing. Use the layer-by-layer preview to see exactly how your print will turn out.</span></p>", 
                    "ElementCode": "LYBPJA", 
                    "Images": [], 
                    "Type": "text"
                }, 
                {
                    "Content": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img title=\"MatterControl Touch T10 - 10.6&quot; Standalone 3D Printer Controller\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/z6LcjwLdtoQxT7OaQIjXt9t_Iroipryh4dl2St1HzAEoAIeDQZpP-TjZC-h4qzpI-RbFLECJlIDUacNqySpjyn4YZvo\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">MatterControl T10 can be used with most 3D Printers</p>", 
                    "ElementCode": "LWDQHE", 
                    "Images": [
                        {
                            "ImageFile": "/mh-product-images/prod/legacy_z6LcjwLdtoQxT7OaQIjXt9t_Iroipryh4dl2St1HzAEoAIeDQZpP-TjZC-h4qzpI-RbFLECJlIDUacNqySpjyn4YZvo", 
                            "ImageUrl": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/dWdamSJEu9oMSc_o63fHoTGNb44WokEZN-pq0d8LJ16A-LcNRKzdCO7eg6434eAJb5jMiQWd_3lKWu5bX27f2KE", 
                            "IsFeatured": false
                        }
                    ], 
                    "Type": "text"
                }, 
                {
                    "Content": "<p><strong>Customizable Settings</strong>&nbsp;- Create and customize your own, or use built-in presets for material and quality settings to make switching filaments simple and convenient. No more failed prints because you forgot to change a setting.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Design Plugins</strong>&nbsp;- Get add-ons to make simple parts right on your printer.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Dual Extrusion / Multi-Material</strong>&nbsp;- Assigning different materials is a snap so you can take full advantage of any multi-extruder equipped 3D printer.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Mid-print Tuning and Adjustment</strong>&nbsp;- Fine tune your prints with on-the-fly adjustments to speed, extrusion rates, and first layer height.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Print History</strong>&nbsp;- Keep a record of your favorite prints so you can reprint your most impressive parts with the click of a button.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Design Library</strong>&nbsp;- Organize all of your 3D printable models in one searchable location for easy access.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Advanced Features</strong>&nbsp;- MatterControl Touch puts the full capability of 3D printing into the hands of power users. So if you want to adjust&nbsp;eeprom&nbsp;settings, create custom macros, or send terminal commands directly to your machine - you can.</p>", 
                    "ElementCode": "BK8HG1", 
                    "Images": [], 
                    "Type": "text"
                }, 
                {
                    "Content": "<h2>What's New?</h2>\r\n<p>MatterControl is an ever-evolving platform here are just a few of the features that have been recently added:</p>\r\n<p><strong>Web-based Camera Monitoring</strong> - Keep an eye on your prints using the onboard camera.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Web-based Control</strong> - Start and stop prints remotely.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cloud Library</strong> - Sync your design files across multiple devices.</p>\r\n<p><strong>X3G Support</strong> - More models are now supported than ever before, including .x3g based printers.</p>\r\n<p>The best part? Any future features will be delivered directly to your MatterControl T10 device. You can participate in this continuously improving experience by providing feedback and letting us know what features you would like to see.</p>", 
                    "ElementCode": "KNK782", 
                    "Images": [], 
                    "Type": "text"
                }, 
                {
                    "Content": "<p style='text-align:center;'><img title='MatterControl Touch T10 - Standalone 3D Printer Controller' src='https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/ZVyN7uC1ZdF1tamixakcDgApAvUcpoA0Gfe9zvhvz-gNBJwTJ_f8bGfJYsvndDQYjvdswaFdc9D2QIVT_2lIQEtuaw'></p>",

                {
                    "Content": "<h2 dir=\"ltr\"><span>Hardware Tech Specs:\u00a0</span></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-de3e4705-135e-117f-783f-19a8dd722f0e\">RAM:\u00a0<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-de3e4705-135f-8317-2099-e1b7ae506da7\">1GB</span></span></li>\n<li><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-de3e4705-135e-27a8-53f7-2a0c0159f513\">CPU: 2GHz Octa-Core</span></li>\n<li><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-de3e4705-135e-27a8-53f7-2a0c0159f513\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-de3e4705-135f-b06e-f33c-e4282fcef90d\">Internal Storage:\u00a0<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-de3e4705-135f-cc26-baf6-4aeb4ec42c74\">16GB</span></span></span></li>\n<li><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-de3e4705-135e-8cdc-a133-3f1b05932d3f\">External Storage: micro<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-de3e4705-135f-f9e7-9d90-92e17d3a2f70\">SD Card</span></span></li>\n<li><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-de3e4705-135e-a7ec-50a6-7a8ecee84ae0\">5.0 megapixel Onboard Camera</span></li>\n<li>IPS Touchscreen</li>\n<li>Wifi-Connectivity</li>\n<li><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-de3e4705-135f-1888-ac9b-8b9338d7d35a\">Standalone Control</span></li>\n<li>Web Monitoring</li>\n<li><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-de3e4705-135f-51f2-07ab-4edadf58bdf4\">Remote Print Start &amp; Stop</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>Check out MatterControl Touch\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.matterhackers.com/articles/mattercontrol-touch-getting-started-guide\" target=\"_blank\">Getting Started Guide</a>.</p>",

                    "Content": "<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong><em>My 3D Printer model isn&rsquo;t listed as supported, will it still work?</em></strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">As a general rule any printer that runs &ldquo;.gcode&rdquo; will work, including custom, and home-built printers.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong><em>Do I need to be connected to the internet or a wifi network for this to work?</em></strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">No. &nbsp;However, MatterControl Cloud Sync features such as web file transfers, remote monitoring, remote controls and auto-updates, do require a wireless internet connection.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong><em>How do I add printable models to my MatterControl Touch?</em></strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">There are several ways to find printable files - you can download files directly to the Touch from the web, transfer files via microSD Card or transfer files wirelessly from your computer via MatterControl Desktop by uploading them to the Cloud Library.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong><em>Can I get the application separately and run it on a standard Android tablet?</em></strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Nope. &nbsp;MatterControl T10 has been modified at the hardware and firmware level in order to act as a dedicated computing device connected over USB. &nbsp;It it important to note that these devices are not meant to work separately from the 3D printer itself.</p>", 
                    "ElementCode": "3SCHKG", 
                    "Images": [], 
                    "Type": "text"
                },
